						"description": "GraphQL query to get student by ID.\n\n**Query:**\n```graphql\nquery {\n  studentById(id: 1) {\n    id\n    name\n    age\n    grade\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- id (ID!): Student's unique identifier (required)\n\n**Return Fields:**\nSelect only the fields you need!"
					},
